node.text: #tbt

Michael played my dad on Boardwalk Empire. I was about to turn 9 in two days and it was my last acting job in NY before I moved to LA to start filming Jessie a month later. When I first met him, I didn’t know what to expect… but I will say he was one of the nicest, kind-hearted people I’ve ever worked with. This industry will not be the same without him. Rest easy Michael K. Williams aka Chalky White 💔
